earthquake survivor julio berumen has 
been flooded with donations toys and getwell cards but the 
6yearold boy still cries out for the one thing no one can give 
him his mother 
she died within inches of him when the upper deck of the nimitz 
freeway slammed down on their car in last weeks earthquake 
