occasionally came into knights classroom to check on her brother 
julio was an enthusiastic kickball player and possessed 
irrepressible energy at an age when many kids are shy knight said 
confident and cheerful he was proceeding well in his bilingual 
studies in english and spanish 
a little while ago i told his mother in a parentteacher 
conference you dont have to worry about julio hes going to be 
fine knight said 
i think i still feel that way with support i expect julio to 
have a full and wonderful life if we all work to help him and his 
father then theres no reason why he cant 
 
