child pornography the most offensive of all and cautioned that 
officials must be sensitive to first amendment protections 
pornography to me is degrading to human dignity in every form 
but it is most degrading to the human dignity of those who are 
innocent and defenseless and who are preyed upon by criminal 
actors thornburgh said 
we must be attentive to the preservation of first amendment 
rights just as we are attentive to the enforcement of laws that 
attack those practices that lie outside the area of first amendment 
protection 
