p casey and officials of the human rights group amnesty 
international said a state police negotiator cpl raul ramos 
casey did not comply 
earlier a huge fire in the education building sent flames 
rising 100 feet in the air and an explosion at or near a prison 
furniture factory rattled windows up to a mile away 
inmates pelted firefighters with rocks 
officials said 12 of 31 prison buildings were destroyed in the 
fires including two commissaries officials had to bring in a 
portable national guard kitchen to provide meals for prisoners not 
