with the afghan government and generally supported president 
najibs attempts to unite the country torn by an 11yearold civil 
war 
we would like to see a broadbased coalition of forces unite 
in this country said the diplomat who spoke on condition of 
anomymity we dont care who is in power that is the internal 
affairs of afghanistan 
