an earthquake registering 71 on the richter scale sent shock 
waves rippling across the 29yearold concrete stadium at 504 
pm oct 17 a capacity crowd of 62000 unaware of the 
devastation it had wrought elsewhere reacted almost with 
merriment chanting lets play ball lets play ball and 
remaining calm until the park was cleared out three hours later 
