from 13 percent other private surveys had similar figures 
their gains have strengthened the possibility of a runoff in 
december between the two top votegetters most likely collor de 
mello on one side and either lula da silva or brizola on the other 
a runoff is called for if no candidate wins a majority nov 15 
the longoutlawed brazilian communist party is in the race for 
