the care project began in 1974 and now aims at changing lives 
not landscapes johnson said massive reforestation projects of the 
1970s and early 1980s failed because they didnt take into account 
the causes of deforestation people have certain very clear needs 
for food fuel and construction wood they are not able to meet 
