him his wife laura patriarca then an attorney with the thrift 
office was offered a job with american continental 
testimony by patriarca and black illustrates keatings wide 
political reach which included persuading five senators whose 
campaigns he had helped fund to meet with regulators on his behalf 
in april 1987 
