plane 
japan air lines has announced it will buy 20 of the new boeing 
747400s widely thought to be the nextgeneration jet plane and 
all nippon airways is planning to purchase another 24 
the main advantage of the 747400 is its fuelsaving features 
which allow the plane to fly 930 miles farther than conventional 
747s 
but the new plane also features an advanced computer system 
which boeing co says makes it possible to fly the 747400 with 
