management bills to be issued the next day 
treasury officials went forward with the borrowing after 
congressional leaders were not forthcoming with assurances that 
congress would be able to pass an extension of the debt legislation 
before the midnight tuesday deadline when the current 287 
trillion debt ceiling drops to 28 trillion 
bradys announcement came in a letter to house republican leader 
